<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/user.css' />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/file-text-fill.svg" type="image/x-icon">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  </head>

  <body class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400">
        <h1 class="bg-green-500 text-slate-300 py-6 text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-center font-bold drop-shadow-sm">
            <p class="">
                Image to Text
                <i class="bi bi-file-text"></i>
            </p>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-bold text-center my-2 text-md sm:text-lg">Converts only those images which has text in it.</p>
        <hr>

        <main class="mx-2 sm:m-6">
            <div class="text-md sm:text-lg mx-5 sm:mx-8">
                <h1 class="text-white text-md -mx-5 sm:text-xl font-bold">
                    Confusion <i class="bi bi-patch-question-fill"></i>, how to create unique files on Laptop?
                </h1>
                <br>
                <ol class="list-decimal">
                    <li>Convert your pdf to images from this site <a href="https://www.ilovepdf.com/pdf_to_jpg" target="_blank" class="text-green-500 hover:underline">pdf to Image</a> and download zip file.</li>
                    <li>Extract the zip file downloaded.</li>
                    <li><strong>Ctrl+A</strong> to select all the image files.</li>
                    <li>Right click on any file(<em>as all files are selected</em>) and select <strong>rename</strong>.</li>
                    <li>Give any name to the file, it will create file name with the unique index on every file. As an example: You gave "hello" it will create "hello (1)" itself.</li>
                    <li>You have 10 files then, it will be named as "hello (1)" ...........up to "hello (10)".</li>
                    <li>Click the <strong> browse/choose files</strong> button below.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <p class="mt-7 sm:mt-10 bg-blue-300 text-blue-800 px-6 w-fit text-md sm:text-md rounded-md py-2 flex border-2 border-blue-800">&nbsp;
                <i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill"></i>&nbsp;<strong>NOTE:</strong>&nbsp;The text generated may not be 100% accurate from the images you provide !!
            </p>

            <div class="border-dashed border-2 border-black-900 mt-3 p-5 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:justify-between">

                <form id="form" class="" action="/converted" autocomplete="off" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">  
                    <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Upload Images Here</p>                  
                    <p class="pb-2 text-md sm:text-lg">1. Select the language that appears in your picture.</p>
                    <select name="language" id="lng" class="text-white mb-4 p-2 rounded-lg bg-gray-600 text-center w-full text-md sm:text-md" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected hidden>-- Choose Language --</option>
                        <option value="1">Nepali</option>
                        <option value="2">English</option>
                    </select>
                    <br>
                    
                    <% if (errorMessage) {%>
                        <p id="error1" class="bg-red-300 text-red-900 text-center py-2 mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-red-800 text-md sm:text-lg" role="alert"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill">&nbsp;</i><%= errorMessage %></p> 
                    <%}%>

                    <p class="text-md sm:text-lg">2. Insert one or more picture files.</p>
                    <input type="file" name="files" id="fileInput" class="mb-4 w-full border-solid border-2 border-black-600 px-2 py-4 rounded-lg file:rounded-md file:border-0 file:bg-green-500 file:py-2 file:px-3 file:text-white file:cursor-pointer file:hover:bg-green-600" multiple required><br>
                    <button id="submitBtn" action="#" class="bg-green-500 w-full text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-white hover:text-green-600 hover:border-solid hover:border-2 hover:border-green-600 cursor-pointer"><a>SUBMIT</a></button><br>
                </form>

                <!-- <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-0 w-full sm:w-1/2">
                    <button class="bg-green-500 text-white text-md sm:text-lg w-full sm:w-1/2 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-white hover:text-green-600 hover:border-solid hover:border-2 hover:border-green-600 cursor-pointer">DOWNLOAD</button>
                </div> -->

            </div>
        </main>

      <footer class="bg-zinc-600 text-white text-center py-10 mt-8">
        &copy; <em>Developed by Sabin Panthi</em>
      </footer>
  </body>
<!-- <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script> -->
<!-- <script src="./public/javascripts/FileSaver.js"></script> -->
</html>
